<subSubSection pageId="56" pageNumber="57" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="56.[151,1436,327,570]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,399,426]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Distribution.</emphasis>
This species was previously recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[856,1003,400,426]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Deeming, J. C. &amp; Al-Dhafer, H. M." box="[1048,1389,400,426]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" pagination="1 - 88" refId="ref28013" refString="Deeming, J. C. &amp; Al-Dhafer, H. M. (2012) Chloropidae from the Arabian Peninsula (Diptera: Cyclorrhapha). Zoology in the Middle East. 58, 1 - 88." type="journal article" year="2012">Deeming &amp; Al-Dhafer (2012)</bibRefCitation>
; El- Hawagry 
<emphasis box="[261,317,436,462]" italics="true" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">et al.</emphasis>
(2016; 2017). It was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[735,808,437,463]" name="Kenya" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Kenya</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[862,963,436,462]" name="Tanzania" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
and is further recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[1294,1389,436,462]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[151,229,473,499]" name="Yemen" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">Yemen</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Deeming, J. C. &amp; Al-Dhafer, H. M." box="[244,565,472,498]" pageId="56" pageNumber="57" pagination="1 - 88" refId="ref28013" refString="Deeming, J. C. &amp; Al-Dhafer, H. M. (2012) Chloropidae from the Arabian Peninsula (Diptera: Cyclorrhapha). Zoology in the Middle East. 58, 1 - 88." type="journal article" year="2012">Deeming &amp; Al-Dhafer 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
